title: Freaks (Scratch Of Scratches)
lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Does it hurt, does it hurt too much?
Have you had enough, are you done?
Are we out, are we out of luck?
Are we giving up, or has it just begun, gun?
[Chorus]
Freaks, is that all we are?
Freaks, twisted and scarred
Freaks, keep us in a jar
But when it goes dark
You know who to call, baby
You know, you know, you know, you know, you know who to call
Mmm, mmm, mmm, mmm, mmm
[Verse 2]
Go ahead, go ahead and cry
I won't wonder why, I know
All the pain, all the pain you hide
I'm your suicide, I'm your ghost
[Chorus]
Freaks, is that all we are?
Freaks, twisted and scarred
Freaks, keep us in a jar
But when it goes dark
You know who to call, baby
You know, you know, you know, you know, you know who to call
Mmm, mmm, mmm, mmm, mmm
